<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="puzzled-adj">puzzled <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pʌzld/    美 /'pʌzld/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>困惑的；迷惑的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She looked puzzled so I repeated the question. 
她看上去很困惑，所以我把问题重复了一遍。</p></div></div>